invalid type: string "...but you can't know for sure.\nYet it doesn't matter.\n- Now, tell me why!\\N- Because you'll be together!\nBut I never knew that that idea\\Nwould grow in her mind like a cancer...\n...that even after she woke....\nThat even after\\Nyou came back to reality...\n...that you'd continue to believe\\Nyour world wasn't real.\nThat death was the only escape.\nMal, no! Jesus!\n\n